    <title>C复习记录1</title>
    <link href="/2022/03/21/C/"/>
    <url>/2022/03/21/C/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="C语言——复习记录1"><a href="#C语言——复习记录1" class="headerlink" title="C语言——复习记录1"></a>C语言——复习记录1</h1><h3 id="1-在计算机内存中，整数一律采用补码形式来存储"><a href="#1-在计算机内存中，整数一律采用补码形式来存储" class="headerlink" title="1.  在计算机内存中，整数一律采用补码形式来存储"></a>1.  在计算机内存中，整数一律采用补码形式来存储</h3><h3 id="2-小数的长度是固定的，float始终占4个字节，double始终占8个字节"><a href="#2-小数的长度是固定的，float始终占4个字节，double始终占8个字节" class="headerlink" title="2.  小数的长度是固定的，float始终占4个字节，double始终占8个字节"></a>2.  小数的长度是固定的，float始终占4个字节，double始终占8个字节</h3><h3 id="3-wchar-t一种“数据类型”"><a href="#3-wchar-t一种“数据类型”" class="headerlink" title="3.  wchar_t一种“数据类型”"></a>3.  wchar_t一种“数据类型”</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- 在微软编译器下，它的长度是2个字节，等价于unsinged short  - 在GCC/LLVM/Clang下，它的长度是4个字节，等价于unsigned int</code></pre></div><h3 id="4-C语言字符编码"><a href="#4-C语言字符编码" class="headerlink" title="4. C语言字符编码"></a>4. C语言字符编码</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- 对于 char 类型的窄字符，始终使用 ASCII 编码。- 对于 wchar_t 类型的宽字符和宽字符串，使用 UTF-16 或者 UTF-32 编码，它们都是基于 Unicode 字符集的。- 对于 char 类型的窄字符串，微软编译器使用本地编码，GCC、LLVM/Clang 使用和源文件编码相同的编码。</code></pre></div><h3 id="5-C语言的输入输出与缓冲区"><a href="#5-C语言的输入输出与缓冲区" class="headerlink" title="5. C语言的输入输出与缓冲区"></a>5. C语言的输入输出与缓冲区</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- 对于输出操作，清空缓冲区会使得缓冲区中的所有数据立即显示到屏幕上；很明显，这些数据没有地方存放了，只能输出了。- 对于输入操作，清空缓冲区就是丢弃残留字符，让程序直接等待用户输入，避免引发奇怪的行为。&gt;清空缓冲区方法：将输入缓冲区中的数据都读取出来。  <figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-comment">//用getchar()清空缓冲区</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> c;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>((c = getchar()) != <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; c != EOF);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h3 id="6-C语言的数组是静态的，大小不可变"><a href="#6-C语言的数组是静态的，大小不可变" class="headerlink" title="6. C语言的数组是静态的，大小不可变"></a>6. C语言的数组是静态的，大小不可变</h3><h3 id="7-数组的越界和溢出"><a href="#7-数组的越界和溢出" class="headerlink" title="7. 数组的越界和溢出"></a>7. 数组的越界和溢出</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- C语言数组是静态的，不能自动扩容，当下标小于零或大于等于数组长度时，就发生了越界。- C语言为了提高效率，保证操作的灵活性，并不会对越界行为进行检查，即使越界了，也能够正常编译，只有在运行期间才可能会发生问题。- &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt; __由于C语言的”放任“，我们访问数组时必须非常小心，要确保不会发生越界。__  &lt;/font&gt;</code></pre></div><h3 id="8-递归"><a href="#8-递归" class="headerlink" title="8. 递归"></a>8. 递归</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- 要想让递归函数逐层进入再逐层退出，需要解决两个方面的问题:    * 存在限制条件，当符合这个条件时递归便不再继续。对于 factorial()，当形参 n 等于 0 或 1 时，递归就结束了。    * 每次递归调用之后越来越接近这个限制条件。对于 factorial()，每次递归调用的实参为 n - 1，这会使得形参 n 的值逐渐减小，越来越趋近于 1 或 0。* 尾递归，中间递归，多层递归，烧脑程度逐级上升。* 递归的时间开销极大，尽量用 __迭代__ 来替换递归函数        <figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;time.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//斐波那契数列，求第n个斐波那契数。</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//递归法</span><br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">func_digui</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <br>    &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> func_digui(n - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) + func_digui(n - <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//迭代法</span><br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">func_diedai</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> p3;<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> p2;<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> p1;<br><br>p2 = p1 = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (n &gt; <span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br>    &#123;<br>        n -= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><br>        p3 = p2;<br>        p2 = p1;<br>        p1 = p2 + p3;<br>    &#125;<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> p1;<br>&#125;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">long</span> res1,res2;<br><br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Input a number: &quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">clock_t</span> time_start_recursion, time_end_recursion;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">clock_t</span> time_start_iteration, time_end_iteration;<br><br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//递归时间</span><br>    time_start_recursion = clock();<br>    res1 = func_digui(n);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result = %ld\n&quot;</span>, res1);<br>    time_end_recursion = clock();<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;run time with recursion: %lfs\n&quot;</span>, (<span class="hljs-type">double</span>)(time_end_recursion - time_start_recursion) / CLOCKS_PER_SEC);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//迭代的时间</span><br>    time_start_iteration = clock();<br>    res2 = func_diedai(n);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result = %ld\n&quot;</span>, res2);<br>    time_end_iteration = clock();<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;run time with iteration: %lfs\n&quot;</span>, (<span class="hljs-type">double</span>)(time_end_iteration - time_start_iteration) / CLOCKS_PER_SEC);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
